<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218189>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 8. Male terminalia of Sphaeronemoura siveci sp. n.; holotype, India, Meghalaya, Nokrek NP — 5: dorsal view; 6: laterodorsal view; 7: ventral view; 8: lateral view — scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218189/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218190>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Type localities of Amphinemura baumanni sp. n. (dot) and Sphaeronemoura siveci sp. n. (ring) — grey areas are above 1000 m, Indian states of published Nemouridae records marked with numbers as follows: 1 — Jammu and Kashmir; 2 — Himachal Pradesh; 3 — Tamil Nadu; 4 — West Bengal; 5 — Meghalaya; 6 — Assam; 7 — Arunachal Pradesh; 8 — Manipur; 9 — Mizoram." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

